    <!--Content-Begin-->
    <article>
            <h1>Oplysning om ændringer i virksomheden</h1>
      <summary>
        <p>
                      
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->

En autoriseret eller godkendt virksomhed er forpligtet til at oplyse Sikkerhedsstyrelsen, hvis der sker ændringer i virksomheden. Læs mere om, hvilke oplysninger Sikkerhedsstyrelsen skal have. Fx når en fagligt ansvarlig tiltræder eller fratræder.
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->
                            </p>
      </summary>
      <div class="pull-right social-icons">
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Autorisation-el-vvs-og-kloak/Autorisation/Oplysning-om-aendringer-i-virksomheden" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square facebook-brand"></i></a>
<a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Autorisation-el-vvs-og-kloak/Autorisation/Oplysning-om-aendringer-i-virksomheden" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter-square twitter-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Autorisation-el-vvs-og-kloak/Autorisation/Oplysning-om-aendringer-i-virksomheden" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-pinterest-square pinterest-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Autorisation-el-vvs-og-kloak/Autorisation/Oplysning-om-aendringer-i-virksomheden" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-linkedin-square linkedin-brand"></i></a>
<a href="mailto:?subject=Oplysning om ændringer i virksomheden&body=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Autorisation-el-vvs-og-kloak/Autorisation/Oplysning-om-aendringer-i-virksomheden" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-envelope-o mail-brand"></i></a>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
</div>
      <br>
      <hr>
        
              
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>En autoriseret eller godkendt virksomhed har oplysningspligt ifølge § 19 i lov om autorisation af virksomheder på el-, vvs- og kloakinstallationsområdet.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="https://www.retsinformation.dk/Forms/R0710.aspx?id=162734" target="_self">Link til lov om autorisation af virksomheder på el-, vvs- og kloakinstallationsområdet</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Det betyder, at virksomheden skal informere Sikkerhedsstyrelsen, når:</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<ul>

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>der sker ændringer i de oplysninger, der er givet til Sikkerhedsstyrelsen ved ansøgningens indsendelse</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>en fagligt ansvarlig fratræder</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>en ny fagligt ansvarlig tiltræder</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>virksomheden ophører fuldstændigt eller</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

<li>virksomheden ikke længere ønsker at være autoriseret eller godkendt.</li>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/li.tpl) -->

</ul>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/ul.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Oplysningerne indgives digitalt via blanket på Virk.dk.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="https://indberet.virk.dk/search/virk/sikkerhedsstyrelsen" title="Link til oplysningsblanket på Virk.dk" target="_self">Link til blanket på Virk.dk</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
      
      
